# The golden corpus (issue #4) is committed reference data produced ONLY by
# scripts/export_golden.py. The globs above (*.csv, and formerly *.log) would
# otherwise swallow its files, so re-include the whole corpus tree. Everything
# under it is intentional and byte-checked in CI; never hand-edit it.
!tests/golden_corpus/**
